channel.title: Praxis Music - With You (Mega Collab) [Future House]
channel.description:
This one was a big one for us, here at Praxis. We had 7 artists, and it took 2 months to complete this.
So, with out further ado...
On the behalf of @Osharu, @Xicon, @FLB100, @joshuatuworldwide, Sib, and myself, I present "[With You](https://fanlink.to/prxswithyou)."
℗ 2018 Praxis Music

item.title: Praxis Music - With You (Mega Collab) [Future House]
item.dc:creator: NickElle
item.description:
Actually, @joshuatuworldwide and I didn’t use Auxy for this track.
We used our DAWs to create, then I used Ableton Live to mix and master.

I did use Live to record my vocals, then I ran them through a processing chain that I created.
